---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

const bookingUrl = 'https://calendar.app.google/rC9Kz37aZANXAUgt5';
---

<Base
  title="You're in — let's talk"
  description="Thanks for telling Jonathan what's next for your agent. Book a free 15-minute call to map your next move."
>
  <div class="container next-page">
    <div class="book-hero panel">
      <p class="book-kicker">What's Next</p>
      <h1>Got it. Now let's make it real.</h1>
      <p class="book-sub">
        You told me where you want to take your agent. The fastest way to get
        there isn't another email thread &mdash; it's 15 minutes with me,
        looking at your actual workflow. Bring the one task you'd most like off
        your plate.
      </p>

      <ul class="book-benefits">
        <li>A clear read on whether your workflow is worth automating</li>
        <li>The specific next step to build it &mdash; or an honest &ldquo;not yet,&rdquo; and why</li>
        <li>No pitch, no slides &mdash; just your work and a plan</li>
      </ul>

      <a href={bookingUrl} class="book-cta">Book your free 15-minute call &rarr;</a>

      <p class="book-reassure">
        Free &middot; 15 minutes &middot; pick any open time that works for you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
